               <t:floruit notAfter="1250" notAfter-iso="1300">He was a 13th-14th century metropolitan of the Ethiopian Orthodox Church and  a contemporary of King <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10303Yekunno">Yǝkunno ʾAmlāk</t:persName>. 
